{"tid":2490162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國 FBI：每10小時便需要就中國展開新調查檔案","createTime":"2021-04-15T11:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T01:01:47.000Z","uid":305299,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1cb2be08662d00ec88909710800dbcf3ed15ca","tid":2490162,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"聯邦調查局局長 Christopher Wray，出席國會參議院情報特別委員會聽證會時，向議員們表示，FBI 每10小時便需要就中國展開新調查任務，並指沒有任何國家比中國對美國的經濟安全和民主理想所構成更大的威脅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFBI opens a new investigation into China 'every 10 hours,' bureau director says<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2021/04/14/politics/fbi-director-china-investigations-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2021%2F04%2F14%2Fpolitics%2Ffbi-director-china-investigations-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=38d61989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2021%2F04%2F14%2Fpolitics%2Ffbi-director-china-investigations-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=0fcf1520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2021/04/14/politics/fbi-director-china-investigations-intl-hnk/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"440df213ec6f128c65af5b47c3034e38a767b610","tid":2490162,"uid":295735,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"又唔係10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48c891a16112f78e0132ca5b506565bab0e00d","tid":2490162,"uid":230530,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強又不點名列出，以「勾結外國勢力」罪名，檢控一名傳媒集團主腦，現正在扣留。他控制的媒體仍然誤導、炒作、不盡不實，挑動市民對政府及國家仇恨，警方已經發出超過130封信對針對警方不確報道作出投訴及澄清。他強調，任何人不論界別，都不能凌駕法律，只要曾經違法、曾經危害國家安全都要為行為找數，他與警隊會繩之以法。<br />\n1<br />\n37"},{"pid":"c8a903dcbaadae42d12c4ae8eb8e99d21454464d","tid":2490162,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl